<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document Share Access Revoked</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #FF5858;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .document-info {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Document Access Revoked</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
      
      <p>This is to inform you that your access to the following document has been revoked:</p>
      
      <div class="document-info">
        <h3>{{documentName}}</h3>
        <p><strong>Document Type:</strong> {{documentType}}</p>
        <p><strong>Case Reference:</strong> {{caseReference}}</p>
        <p><strong>Originally shared by:</strong> {{senderName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Revocation reason:</strong> {{revocationReason}}</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>The previously shared link will no longer work, and you won't be able to access this document anymore.</p>
      
      <p>If you believe this is a mistake or have any questions, please contact {{senderName}} directly.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The Immigration Platform Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Immigration Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

